<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هِيَ دُرَّتِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَلِمَ الْوَرَى أَنَّ الْوُصُولَ إِلَى النُّجُومِ سَيَسْهُلُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَمَّا الْوُصُولُ لِنَظْرَةٍ مِنْ دُرَّتِي لا يُعْقَلُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ذَا مُسْتَحِيلْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَلأَتْ عُيُونِي صِرْتُ أَعْمَى عَنْ سِوَاهَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَنَا إِنْ نَظَرْتُ لِغَيْرِهَا سَيَلُومُنِي قَلْبِي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَتَعْصِي نَظْرَتِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فِي الْقَلْبِ تَسْكُنُ فِي الْحَنَايَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>سَتَقَرُّ فِي أَعْمَاقِ رُوحِي بَيْنَ نَفْسِ وَمُهْجَتِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* * *<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>قَالُوا تَمَهَّلْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِنْ تَجِدْهَا كَيْفَ تَاتِي بِالثَّمَنْ؟<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لَكِنَّنِي لَنْ أَنْتَظِرْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>